2026-05-16T05:35:33.8970528Z 248            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-16T05:35:33.8971425Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-16T05:35:33.8972189Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-16T05:35:33.8972935Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T05:35:33.8973658Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-16T05:35:33.8974358Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-16T05:35:33.8975367Z 254            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
