2026-05-16T05:35:34.4589517Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-16T05:35:34.4589869Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-16T05:35:34.4590221Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
